{"tid":2140479,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被捕反綁坐地 醫生：警想侮辱醫護","createTime":"2020-08-05T04:46:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T05:11:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c3bca579684cbe2a64ac792934317bb83d62f986","tid":2140479,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:46:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/WJIBMZR7DF3O2ILM5BEH6MOPFE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FWJIBMZR7DF3O2ILM5BEH6MOPFE%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7ZeapBhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=5e1c7704\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FWJIBMZR7DF3O2ILM5BEH6MOPFE%2F&h=73c3587c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/WJIBMZR7DF3O2ILM5BEH6MOPFE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n被捕反綁坐地 醫生：警想侮辱醫護<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9XoQZpxQg5a_CA8LyfHajir4SyM=/190x142/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MY46ZX4PDEQPCNRGRVHEYK4LVI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9XoQZpxQg5a_CA8LyfHajir4SyM%3D%2F190x142%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMY46ZX4PDEQPCNRGRVHEYK4LVI.jpg&h=153b16b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n抗爭運動以來人道救援者屢遭警暴；圖為去年理大一役醫護人員被反綁雙手等候拘捕。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】「一位體形龐大的示威者被制服時，嘔吐出透明液體，急救隊員從示威者朋友口中得知，示威者有心臟病。除了急救員，現場還有一位醫生。嘔吐透明液體可以是脊髓受損的徵狀，急救隊員因此嘗試向示威者施救。急救員向警員展示急救證件，但警員看也沒看拒絕要求，表示無法證明他的身份。急救員於是向警方表示有一位醫生在場，但警方亦沒有理會。」這是一名急救員去年10月27日示威現場的親身經歷。APPG報告臚列了大量急救員的證詞，顯示香港警方處理反送中運動期間的橫蠻無理。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。他當時身穿一般衣着，沒有展示暴力，身上帶有急救用品，但仍被警方用索帶反綁雙手，與大群被捕人士坐在地上一、兩小時。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n義工施救中胡椒球彈<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：報告詳列人道救援者受侵犯  林鄭PK鄧縱容警暴 英跨黨派促制裁<br />\n<br />\n另一個戰場中文大學，去年11月曾遭警方猛攻。一名急救員的供詞顯示，警方為了佔據二號橋，向該處一個急救站發射大量催淚彈，當時仍有受傷的學生及示威者正接受治理。<br />\n<br />\n醫生說：「我感到警方想藉此侮辱醫護人員，當警員靠近我時，我告訴他們我是一間醫院的醫生，並向他們展示職員證，但警方仍然表示以暴動罪名拘捕我。」。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n更嚴重的暴力發生在運動後期，報告引述另一急救員的供詞指出，今年2月9日凌晨時分，多名身穿急救背心的急救員在將軍澳富康花園籃球場治理受傷示威者，多名警員在毫無預警下進入掃射十至二十發胡椒球彈。作供的急救員胸部及右手手腕被擊中。"},{"pid":"9b57bc88ae581a50578878b573310c4c8b33a027","tid":2140479,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:51:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"beb119408a6aa244337173184a98b3a6cdaaaf89","tid":2140479,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:52:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0fc9315b1222597795515c0e6e0397770fbfbe36","tid":2140479,"uid":126626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:57:35.000Z","msg":"永不原諒"},{"pid":"dc470e8b1c6ba8c216474ec141a66b0e63cde28d","tid":2140479,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:58:10.000Z","msg":"地球人都一定要侮辱中共"},{"pid":"f76eca4bc5b6cd7c508efe59f4a8ac9ff45522e5","tid":2140479,"uid":301139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:59:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1b28846edc484d0113c78192055026a75d9dd8ee","tid":2140479,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T04:59:27.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fa88e0cecd2dcb39f3573a80e6d45b5749d236cc","tid":2140479,"uid":156073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:00:22.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"f222778d067c05bae010fbb96bbd3be4fc672fc1","tid":2140479,"uid":156073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:00:39.000Z","msg":"721 831 101 111"},{"pid":"d4439806ab98386b28556b185b6d9601824ad82c","tid":2140479,"uid":48609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T05:01:03.000Z","msg":"黑警有事唔好搵醫生<br />\n神打上身算鳩數啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e1